Class Data

class

Data

classdesc

The constructor of the Data object. This object is used for requesting data from Sitefinity.

param

An object containing configuration options for the Data object.

param

Your service url that points to the configured instance of Sitefinity service.

param

The url name of the type.

param

An object containing configuration options for requests.

param

The provider name to use in each request.

param

The culture name to use in each request.

    data.update({ key: '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000', // key of item to update data: newsItemUpdate, saveTemp: true, successCb: successCb, failureCb: failureCb });
